{"data":[{"date":"15:11 01/08","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p khoe si\u00eau xe Ferrari khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Man City","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/tuyen-thu-phap-khoe-sieu-xe-ferrari-khi-tro-lai-hoi-quan-cung-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Mendy m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Les Bleus b\u1eb1ng Ferrari F2X m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng ch\u00f3e.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ng\u00e0y 31/7, Mendy l\u00e1i Ferrari F2X tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 300.000 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Man City. X\u1ebf h\u1ed9p c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam g\u00f3i \u0111\u1ed9 carbon tr\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thao h\u01a1n. Mendy l\u00e0 t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u xe Italy. Anh t\u1eebng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u model c\u1ee7a Ferrari.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p khoe si\u00eau xe Ferrari khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p khoe si\u00eau xe Ferrari khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/cc-7388-1533088760.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mendy s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City. \u1ea2nh: TS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i m\u0169 Burberry c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, di\u1ec7n \u00e1o kho\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u1ed5 ba m\u00e0u xanh, \u0111\u1ecf, tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1edd Ph\u00e1p, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i, Mendy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho Man City trong ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Mendy k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup di\u1ec5n ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Mendy quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Manchester t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. HLV Guardiola k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay sau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn v\u00ec g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/cc2-9953-1533088760.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4937","checkdouble":"192477"},{"date":"15:22 01/08","title":"Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Barcelona","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/lionel-messi-va-dong-doi-lang-le-ve-hoi-quan-o-barcelona.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4936","checkdouble":"192480"},{"date":"15:27 01/08","title":"B\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson qua l\u1eddi k\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y c\u0169","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/buoc-ngoat-doi-doi-thu-mon-alisson-qua-loi-ke-thay-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh Alisson c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u201cc\u00f2\u201d \u0111\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0y thay v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p t\u1eeb HLV c\u0169 Daniel Pavan. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ra s\u1ee9c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u201cv\u1eeba l\u00f9n, v\u1eeba b\u00e9o\u201d c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo ti\u1ebfp nghi\u1ec7p gi\u1eef g\u00f4n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Alisson v\u1ed1n\u2026 v\u1eeba l\u00f9n, v\u1eeba b\u00e9o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Pavan l\u00e0 HLV tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Alisson t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Internacional tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta x\u00f4n xao chuy\u1ec7n Alisson t\u1eebng su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tan m\u1ed9ng gi\u1eef g\u00f4n v\u00ec\u2026 l\u1edbn ch\u1eadm. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 15 tu\u1ed5i, anh v\u1eabn th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Gi\u1edd Pavan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00eam r\u1eb1ng h\u1ed3i \u1ea5y Alisson kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00f9n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u00e9o n\u1eefa.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson qua l\u1eddi k\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson qua l\u1eddi k\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/pavan1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Pavan \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong vi\u1ec7c Alisson kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf d\u1edf nghi\u1ec7p gi\u1eef g\u00f4n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 13 n\u0103m m\u00e0 Alisson \u1edf Internacional, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 n\u0103m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. N\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ai hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Alisson r\u00f5 h\u01a1n t\u00f4i\u201d, Pavan k\u1ec3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo l\u1eddi k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Pavan, Alisson th\u1eddi ni\u00ean thi\u1ebfu r\u1ea5t m\u00ea b\u00e1nh ng\u1ecdt v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ecdt. \u0102n u\u1ed1ng s\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ed3m n\u00ean Alisson ph\u00e1t ph\u00ec. Alisson tr\u00f4ng c\u00e0ng b\u00e9o b\u1edfi chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 15 tu\u1ed5i, anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 cao 1m70. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c v\u1eeba l\u00f9n v\u1eeba b\u00e9o khi\u1ebfn Alisson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ea1nh tranh so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb h\u1ed3i \u1ea5y \u0111ang ganh \u0111ua su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Internacional c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 t\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i M\u1ed9t t\u1ea1i Internacional.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n15 tu\u1ed5i, Alisson th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Internacional. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Alisson c\u00f3 l\u00fac c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y n\u1ea3n. Nh\u01b0ng Pavan v\u1eabn ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Alisson v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec u\u1ed1n n\u1eafn cho anh. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5y, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng Pavan h\u01a1i g\u00e0n d\u1edf khi c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o anh ch\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1eeba l\u00f9n, v\u1eeba b\u00e9o nh\u01b0 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPavan c\u00f3 c\u00e1i l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf Alisson ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 Alisson ch\u01b0a ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u1ebft. Anh ch\u1ec9 l\u1edbn ch\u1eadm so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ee9 anh ch\u01b0a l\u1edbn h\u1ebft t\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Pavan thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Internacional ch\u1edd Alisson l\u1edbn th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho anh hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pavan (thu hai tu phai sang) chuc mung Alisson trong mot dip anh duoc vinh danh\" title=\"Pavan (th\u1ee9 hai t\u1eeb ph\u1ea3i sang) ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Alisson trong m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/pavan2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pavan (th\u1ee9 hai t\u1eeb ph\u1ea3i sang) ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Alisson trong m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7y \u201ctr\u00e1i l\u1ec7nh\u201d ph\u1ee5 huynh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Internacional xong th\u00ec Pavan g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c. Tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i t\u1eeb b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Alisson. Pavan k\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp: \u201cM\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u1ecd, b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Alisson t\u00ecm g\u1eb7p t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng Alisson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u00ec v\u1edbi nghi\u1ec7p gi\u1eef g\u00f4n c\u1ea3. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n xin cho con trai m\u00ecnh r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi l\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Internacional. B\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Alisson nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng con trai h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e8n s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc h\u00e0nh\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i \u1ea5y l\u00e0 v\u00ec xu\u1ea5t th\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Alisson. So v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean x\u1ee9 Samba, Alisson n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i \u201cm\u1eabu s\u1ed1 chung\u201d con nh\u00e0 ngh\u00e8o. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh anh thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0103n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ec3. B\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Alisson tuy c\u0169ng l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u1eaft g\u00f4n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty \u00f4ng. Ngh\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ed1 Alisson l\u00e0 kinh doanh \u0111\u1ed3 da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 gi\u00e0y d\u00e9p. M\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Alisson tuy h\u1ed3i \u0111i h\u1ecdc c\u0169ng l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e9m c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 sau theo ngh\u1ec1 m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson gio la sieu sao voi su nghiep hoanh trang va ban gai xinh nhu mong\" title=\"Alisson gi\u1edd l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i xinh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/pavan3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alisson gi\u1edd l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i xinh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 Alisson h\u1ed3i \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng con trai m\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 sau theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kinh doanh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Pavan kh\u00f4ng cam t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ef1c y\u00eau qu\u00fd v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u201cb\u1ebb l\u00e1i\u201d nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Pavan ra s\u1ee9c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 Alisson cho Alisson th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMay sao b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 Alisson xu\u00f4i tai nghe theo Pavan. V\u00e0 may n\u1eefa l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m, Alisson cao th\u00eam 17cm v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng gi\u1eef g\u00f4n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Pavan ng\u00e0y \u1ea5y, ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Xa m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng c\u00e1ch l\u00f2ng</em><br>\r\nAlisson \u0111\u00e3 xa l\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Internacional kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u v\u00e0 \u0111ang th\u00e0nh danh b\u00ean tr\u1eddi \u00c2u xa x\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Pavan cho bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pavan \u2013 Alisson v\u1eabn gi\u1eef m\u1ed1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4935","checkdouble":"192481"},{"date":"12:25 01/08","title":"Juventus l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 b\u00e1n Higuain cho AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/14/juventus-len-tieng-vu-ban-higuain-cho-ac-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Giuseppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Higuanin \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi AC Milan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Juventus trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, song s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo bu\u1ed9c anh ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Juventus-len-tieng-vu-Gonzalo-Higuain-toi-AC-Milan--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t c\u1ef1u sao Napoli nh\u1ea5t, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169\u00a0\u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a AC Milan. H\u00f4m qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin Higuain \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m th\u1ee9 2 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p 3 b\u00ean gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Higuain, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Leonardo c\u1ee7a AC Milan v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Higuain. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 18 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin Higuain \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a AC Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Giuseppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain se lai nhuong san khau cho Ronaldo\" title=\"Higuain s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u cho Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Higuain v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft c\u1ea3, Higuain v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHiguain c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016, trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t anh ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Juventus b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 khi Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Juventus, b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho CR7. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4934","checkdouble":"192462"},{"date":"17:28 01/08","title":"HLV Roma c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Malcom","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/hlv-di-francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-roma-mua-hut-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u1ecdn Barcelona ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea1n l\u1eddi v\u1edbi Malcom</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAS Roma \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Robin Olsen, Javier Pastore v\u00e0 Justin Kluivert. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Giallorossi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 Radja Nainggolan v\u00e0 Alisson ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang ra Roma \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux. \u0110\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, ra m\u1eaft cho Malcom. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c, c\u1ea3 Bordeaux v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u201cl\u1eadt k\u00e8o\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/HLV-Di-Francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-Roma-mua-hut-Malcom-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Malcom \u0111\u00e3 \"l\u1eadt k\u00e8o\" v\u1edbi Roma \u0111\u1ec3 sang Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Eusebio Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn khi m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Barca l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n. N\u1ebfu Barcelona mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Malcom, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Barcelona, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec kh\u00e1c\u201d, Di Francesco n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roma Di Francesco\" title=\"HLV Roma Di Francesco\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/hlv-di-francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-roma-mua-hut-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Roma ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 Malcom, HLV Di Francesco cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Roma m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u00ecnh to\u201d, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roma n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 AS Roma tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-roma-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192427.html\">Barca 2-4 Roma (KT): M\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Giallorossi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-hang-hot-bailey-172-192291.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\">Roma nh\u1eafn Barca: \u201cMu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf qua v\u1ee5 Malcom, v\u1eady \u0111\u01b0a Messi \u0111\u00e2y\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-chuan-bi-khoi-kien-bordeaux-vi-lat-keo-vu-malcom-184-191956.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux v\u00ec l\u1eadt k\u00e8o v\u1ee5 Malcom</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4933","checkdouble":"192485"},{"date":"17:49 01/08","title":"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh CLB HAGL l\u1eabn \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2018h\u00edp\u2019 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cho t\u1edbi t\u01b0 duy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. L\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam song ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n khi tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i: \"Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a b\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi. Ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ai s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ai s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Indonesia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y: \"S\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u00e0n anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao, l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf CLB. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 c\u00e1c anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00fap b\u1ecdn em h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y c\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat \u00e1p l\u1ef1c: \"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp trung l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao khi\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u00ean 100% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng coi gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. \"Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m cho \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao. Ai c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn giao h\u1eefu\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 U23 Palestine, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng: \"Palestine l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Palestine s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh cao to, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 6, 3/8. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad-168-192438.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad-168-192438.html\">H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam-168-192391.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam-168-192391.html\">BLV Quang Huy: VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 do hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD v\u00ec gi\u00e1 cao, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Quang Huy cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4932","checkdouble":"192487"},{"date":"16:00 01/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/17/dong-doi-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, PSG chi 222 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar t\u1eeb Barca. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/Javier-Pastore-phat-bieu-ve-Neymar-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-neymar-gia-350-trieu-euro-180-188122.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Neymar</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus. Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 290 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Neymar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar PSG\" title=\"Neymar PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/dong-doi-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o Neymar r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh\u00a0ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNeymar \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh sau khi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Neymar s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar ghi 19 b\u00e0n sau 20 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Song v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Brazil b\u1ecb B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4931","checkdouble":"192479"},{"date":"13:11 01/08","title":"Real nh\u1eafm 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/real-nham-2-sao-khung-nhat-ngoai-hang-anh-nang-cap-hang-cong.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Harry Kane trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real kh\u00f4ng chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Hazard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3\u201d. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cM\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bernabeu\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Salah v\u00e0 Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Salah v\u00e0 Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-chuyen-huong-sang-Salah-va-Kane-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng Real s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f4ng khai \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb song Chelsea t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991, song Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a The Blues, Hazard s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard-180-192441.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Eden Hazard</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Kane ho\u1eb7c Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Harry Kane trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Real Madrid 2018 chuyen huong sang Kane va Salah\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Kane v\u00e0 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/real-nham-2-sao-khung-nhat-ngoai-hang-anh-nang-cap-hang-cong.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Kane v\u00e0 Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Salah l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Kane x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSalah v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool trong khi \u0111\u00f3 HLV Pochettino tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd gi\u1eef Kane b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. Theo El Pais, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Salah ho\u1eb7c Kane.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t trong hai m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Liverpool ho\u1eb7c Tottenham nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4930","checkdouble":"192466"},{"date":"13:26 01/08","title":"Thua M.U, HLV Real v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Vinicius Junior. \u00d4ng khen ng\u1ee3i sao tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man United t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Man United t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Hard Rock, M\u1ef9, Real Madrid tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. V\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t song ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 Karim Benzema, Gareth Bale ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh do m\u1edbi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0 Isco hay Toni Kroos\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, Real d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n song t\u1ecf ra k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ander Herrera v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez. B\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 1-2 c\u1ee7a Benzema l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Real l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Vinicius v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Vinicius v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Vinicius v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui ca ng\u1ee3i Vinicius</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTri\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HLV Julen Lopetegui t\u1ea1i Real \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Vinicius Junior v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng m\u1ef9 t\u1eeb. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real tin r\u1eb1ng sao tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Flamengo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng t\u1eeb m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n\u201cVinicius \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ra s\u00e2n h\u00f4m nay\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cBan \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung, Vinicius \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o s\u00e1ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi, Real s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Benfica tr\u00ean s\u00e2n FedEx Field.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Real:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/Mu-2-1-real.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4929","checkdouble":"192468"},{"date":"14:22 01/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/odriozola-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alvaro Odriozola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Real. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Odriozola gia nh\u1eadp Real</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Odriozola sinh ra t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 ven bi\u1ec3n San Sebastian thu\u1ed9c x\u1ee9 Basque. N\u0103m 2006 t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi l\u00ean 10 tu\u1ed5i, anh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho CLB qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Real Sociedad.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 7 n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 4 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, Odriozola c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Sociedad v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2017. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang m\u00f9a 2017/18, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5t nh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anoeta v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ai ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Odriozola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Odriozola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Odriozola-phat-bieu-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alvaro Odriozola t\u1edbi Real gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra, Odriozola c\u00f3 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nhanh nh\u1eb9n m\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Odriozola l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh Real Madrid v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Real v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Julen Lopetegui, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Odriozola l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, Los Blancos b\u1ecf ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro mang anh v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Sociedad (35 tri\u1ec7u tr\u1ea3 ngay, 5 tri\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, Odriozola \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Odriozola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Real v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o tr\u1eafng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Odriozola Real vs MU\" title=\"hau ve Odriozola Real vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/odriozola-phat-bieu-sau-tran-mu-21-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Odriozola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i&rdquo;, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean h\u00f4m nay, m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o to l\u1edbn. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Karim Benzema hay Gareth Bale, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Real:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/Mu-2-1-real.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4928","checkdouble":"192470"},{"date":"16:00 01/08","title":"Valverde \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Valverde khen ng\u1ee3i Malcom. T\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi AS Roma.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Malcom th\u00edch \u1ee9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMalcom c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Barcelona \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. Anh v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. S\u00e1ng nay, Malcom \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc AS Roma t\u1ea1i ICC v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Malcom \u0111\u00e3 \u201cl\u1eadt k\u00e8o\u201d v\u1edbi Roma ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t. Anh v\u00e0 Bordeaux \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd giao k\u00e8o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia song sau c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Barcelona. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 chi t\u1edbi 41 tri\u1ec7u Euro, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Roma v\u00e0 \u201cc\u01b0\u1edbp\u201d Malcom v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde khen ng\u1ee3i Malcom, t\u00e2n binh Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Valverde khen ng\u1ee3i Malcom, t\u00e2n binh Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/HLV-Valverde-khen-ngoi-Malcom,-tan-binh-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Malcom ghi b\u00e0n cho Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, Malcom th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa gieo s\u1ea7u cho Roma. Anh ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 cho Barca \u1edf ph\u00fat 49. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Blaugrana tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ghi li\u1ec1n 3 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 78 t\u1edbi 86 \u0111\u1ec3 thua chung cu\u1ed9c 2-4.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m x\u00f3a m\u1edd \u0111i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 Malcom t\u1ea1o n\u00ean. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 3 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV valverde\" title=\"HLV valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde khen ng\u1ee3i Malcom</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua Roma, HLV Ernesto Valverde khen ng\u1ee3i Malcom. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\u201d, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca n\u00f3i. \u201cMalcom l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec s\u1ef1 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng nhanh c\u1ee7a Malcom. CLB lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Malcom b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barcelona 2-4 Roma:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/barca-2-4-roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4927","checkdouble":"192474"},{"date":"17:04 01/08","title":"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/15/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-viec-real-mua-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois. T\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Courtois hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm Courtois thay Navas</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas. N\u0103m 2015, su\u00fdt n\u1eefa Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 David De Gea t\u1eeb Man United n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecfng m\u00e1y fax hy h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, M.U v\u1eabn d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 De Gea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Real ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Alisson hay Thibaut Courtois. Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Liverpool l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Real l\u00e0 Courtois.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-viec-real-mua-courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois thay Navas</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. C\u00f3 tin Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i giao k\u00e8o c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Real mang v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb Andriy Lunin t\u1eeb Zorya (Ukraine). C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Keylor Navas l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 1 trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 Kiko Casilla, HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111ang t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea5y m\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ra mat CLB Hoang gia sau khi bi sa thai\" title=\"Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Real Madrid\u201d, Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real khi h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kiko Casilla v\u00e0 Andriy Lunin m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-nham-2-sao-khung-nhat-ngoai-hang-anh-nang-cap-hang-cong-172-192466.html\">Real nh\u1eafm 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard-180-192441.html\">CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund-180-192424.html\">T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Dortmund</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/co-hay-khong-viec-real-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian-180-192421.html\">C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4926","checkdouble":"192483"},{"date":"14:49 01/08","title":"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/chelsea-san-sang-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-gonzalo-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn Higuain kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i, anh kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. AC Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Vuot-mat-AC-Milan,-Chelsea-muon-mua-Gonzalo-Higuain-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0a tin AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Gonzalo Higuain. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 16 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a sau \u0111\u00f3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 ng\u00e0y, t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp 3 b\u00ean gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Higuain, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Leonardo c\u1ee7a AC Milan v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n Higuain \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-len-tieng-vu-ban-higuain-cho-ac-milan-176-192462.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan</span>. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Giuseppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Juventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft c\u1ea3, Higuain v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan v\u1ee5 Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 AC Milan v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Higuain, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Khi m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng qua th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/chelsea-san-sang-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-gonzalo-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan v\u1ee5 Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, Chelsea t\u00ednh ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb Higuain, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Chelsea t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn 2 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb AC Milan.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Stamford Bridge, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, Morata ho\u1eb7c Giroud s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4925","checkdouble":"192472"}]}